<paragraph id="01233780D980A97EA486AFAD932375A0" pageId="0" pageNumber="319">
Figure 1. 
<normalizedToken id="E2BAEF33C191F4D640DADA41E22120DA" originalValue="a–d">a-d</normalizedToken>
Diagnostic sexual features of 
