a Detail of the nodose RTA surface on male palp b Tibial trichobothria on male palp (indicated by an arrow) c Glandular head on spermatheca d Walnut-shaped spermatheca e, f Photos of live specimens of 
<taxonomicName id="88780A6B9A50BB8CD9112F4AE36DC5FE" class="Arachnida" family="Thomisidae" genus="Sidymella" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Sidymella lucida" order="Araneae" pageId="0" pageNumber="319" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="lucida">Sidymella lucida</taxonomicName>
