</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="913AE82A0E4F426898F304E8AD1B98E2" pageId="0" pageNumber="319" type="composition">
<paragraph id="D436B2CD963999D2B48FF773420EC2A4" pageId="0" pageNumber="319">Composition.</paragraph>
<paragraph id="1193773A508DCFC7752427C245BEFD9A" pageId="0" pageNumber="319">
Six Neotropical species: 
<taxonomicName id="12E26B5B0214F800D14DAE8FECBBBA67" class="Arachnida" family="Thomisidae" genus="Sidymella" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Sidymella excavata" order="Araneae" pageId="0" pageNumber="319" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="excavata">Sidymella excavata</taxonomicName>
sp. nov., 
<taxonomicName id="FFA3498EA4C3E6595E0664CD0FE00EA1" genus="S." lsidName="S. furcillata" pageId="0" pageNumber="319" rank="species" species="furcillata">S. furcillata</taxonomicName>
(Keyserling, 1880), 
<taxonomicName id="A848DAADD82C9E0E63AB7343DD26BE2A" genus="S." lsidName="S. longispina" pageId="0" pageNumber="319" rank="species" species="longispina">S. longispina</taxonomicName>
(
<normalizedToken id="E7EC4C1F773DBB0A4581CFBB732AE2E2" originalValue="Mello-Leitão">Mello-Leitao</normalizedToken>
, 1943), 
<taxonomicName id="DE3FABAC6E64596579F3330B0425CDC4" genus="S." lsidName="S. lucida" pageId="0" pageNumber="319" rank="species" species="lucida">S. lucida</taxonomicName>
(Keyserling, 1880), 
<taxonomicName id="72E25395E3CEB2F5260ABDECC457A810" genus="S." lsidName="S. marmorata" pageId="0" pageNumber="319" rank="species" species="marmorata">S. marmorata</taxonomicName>
sp. nov., and 
<taxonomicName id="F2EB01E36498D6E46380B16859F96057" genus="S." lsidName="S. kolpogaster" pageId="0" pageNumber="319" rank="species" species="kolpogaster">S. kolpogaster</taxonomicName>
(Lise, 1973); 11 additional species from the Australasian region that are not within the scope of the present study.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="BD1E7D342CB155B33AF498981FD8B567" pageId="0" pageNumber="319" type="distribution">
<paragraph id="6BBE6A1945D645A3D542F810F58CCA36" pageId="0" pageNumber="319">Distribution.</paragraph>
<paragraph id="127F3859791E5C9E250FABB777C5866D" pageId="0" pageNumber="319">Ecuador, Colombia, Peru, Brazil, Argentina, and Uruguay (Fig. 15).</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
